<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Reservation Confirmed!</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</p>
    <p>We are excited to confirm your reservation at <strong>Kaon Ta!</strong></p>
    
    <div style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #f9f9f9;">
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @table.start_time.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
      <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @table.start_time.strftime("%H:%M") %></p>
      <p><strong>Guests:</strong> <%= @reservation.guest_count %></p>
    </div>

    <p>If you need to make changes, please visit your dashboard.</p>
    
    <p>
      <%= link_to "View My Reservations", reservations_url, style: "background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
    </p>

    <p>See you soon!</p>
  </body>
</html>
